    "Details": "The 70 ton JM7-A slightly modifies the JM7-D to create a cheaper variant. Keeping the Ultra AC/5 and one of the ER Large Lasers, but replacing the remaining weapons with just two Medium Lasers allows the 'Mech to drop its cost by over 3 million c-bills.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Anti-Air Targeting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
